{"tid":2283412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李玟遭網友質疑是新加坡籍    直接回懟：中國香港人","createTime":"2020-11-12T14:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T14:28:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8ca7f5e4b3fd1d0707e10d68bb85dc7205e6cd","tid":2283412,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/204/w630h374/20201111/71fe-kcunqzc8257361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F204%2Fw630h374%2F20201111%2F71fe-kcunqzc8257361.jpg&h=52e42b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月10日，李玟在社交平臺曬出和二姐李思林同框一起跳舞的短視頻。視頻中，兩位女神穿着夾克配墨鏡扮酷，伴隨着音樂節奏點跳舞扭動，本以爲能給大家帶來驚喜，可沒想到網友卻醉翁之意不在酒，在留言中問起了李玟的國籍問題。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在評論區問到了李玟的國籍問題：&ldquo;你是中國人？還是新加坡人？&rdquo;李玟看到之後直接霸氣回懟：&ldquo;我是中國香港人&rdquo;。李玟霸氣的回答令網友們稱讚不已，紛紛誇讚道：&ldquo;女神真霸氣&rdquo;、&ldquo;滿分回答&rdquo;，還指責質疑者&ldquo;沒事找事&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"84cbfc3f6d074310489b29e175b4f8c946cf4b64","tid":2283412,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"玻奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f6daefe7d3502f5aff0e0fefb2e11a80684caf","tid":2283412,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"1e9259f596783523e0b8af79a669e3a810055d63","tid":2283412,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"國籍：美國<br />\n<br />\n向美國舉報呢個八婆共諜"},{"pid":"9787bacec7872d815888d42348117ef9ff87345e","tid":2283412,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"DQ佢本新加坡passport"},{"pid":"9ed77583f70796851a86290b6fa7b44fefdf6be7","tid":2283412,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"以為拎美籍係台灣搵食"},{"pid":"cf989ad0dc48bbe82e72a6f3b4df7a8f12af30b5","tid":2283412,"uid":200083,"like":